{"tid":844030,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"馮翠娟女士先係最高質Youtuber，沒有之一💁🏻‍♂️","createTime":"2018-10-01T14:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T07:14:55.000Z","uid":154793,"like":180,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"96f5e8d2dee7db8efee7699949f4ddf5fb4cbf3f","tid":844030,"uid":154793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"馮翠娟<br />\n係我聽過最高質嘅香港唱作女歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[你是吸煙者] 是一首警世勵志歌曲，<br />\n用蕩氣迴腸的曲風對吸煙者提出血的控訴，<br />\n教育我們的下一代要遠離煙害，<br />\n否則會生cancer死。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m4Ji_Qe_3Vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm4Ji_Qe_3Vw&d=9MYsJ7ZD%2B279ssC7TQbG%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b386c7c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m4Ji_Qe_3Vw</a><br />\n<br />\n[我唔介意冇晒朋友］<br />\n表達馮女士對友人趨炎附勢表裡不一的不屑，<br />\n曲中意境波瀾壯闊，<br />\n可見作者憤世嫉俗的豪情氣概，<br />\n寧願獨善其身，孤身走佢嘅人生路，<br />\n也不願與hi bye fd 隨波逐流志趣相投。<br />\nMV別出心裁，<br />\n以走馬燈形式公開友人的合照，<br />\n暗諷此情不再，快啲釘蓋。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L7g8YGHBTl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL7g8YGHBTl0&d=9MYsJ7ZD%2B279ssC7TQbG%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b292b128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L7g8YGHBTl0</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他單曲如<br />\n「掟晒佢地出火車」「錢錢錢」<br />\n推介比廣大嘅市民，<br />\n同我一齊進入翠娟的音樂小宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7592d829b8024cc870244117134e11070cf33a1d","tid":844030,"uid":154793,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:25:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得佢唱腔好獨特<br />\n好似米雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bddc3e2d3c5ca3f41cc6d30278d81b56999511","tid":844030,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"好好聽"},{"pid":"afde33bdc3b0f33777c4a0a4a18add35cbec3090","tid":844030,"uid":71154,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"75